<anchor id="pdata_8h_1pdata"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The data mamager received metrics and measurement data from various tasks in the system, build the JSON strings for metrics and measurement topic and send these strings to the MQTT connnector task, which publish them to the MQTT broker. See <ref refid="mqtt__connector_8h_1mqtt_connector" kindref="member">mqtt_connector</ref>.</para>
</simplesect>
